      "target": "ASSET_TYPE",

      "transformation": "CASE WHEN A.VEHICLE_TYPE IN ('TRAILER','EQUIPMENT') THEN CAST('EQUIPMENT' AS VARCHAR(50)) WHEN A.VEHICLE_TRIM IN ('TRAILER','EQUIPMENT') THEN CAST('EQUIPMENT' AS VARCHAR(50)) WHEN A.VEHICLE_TYPE IS NULL AND (A.GVWR IS NULL OR A.GVWR = 0) AND A.VEHICLE_TRIM IS NULL AND A.MARKET_CLASS IS NULL THEN CAST('EQUIPMENT' AS VARCHAR(50)) WHEN A.GVWR BETWEEN 1 AND 16000 AND COALESCE(A.VEHICLE_TYPE,'') <> ('EQUIPMENT') THEN CAST('CAR' AS VARCHAR(50)) WHEN (A.GVWR IS NULL OR A.GVWR = 0) AND A.VEHICLE_TYPE IN ('CARS','SUVS','CARGO VANS','CROSSOVERS','LIGHT DUTY TRUCKS','MINIVANS') THEN CAST('CAR' AS VARCHAR(50)) WHEN A.GVWR BETWEEN 16001 AND 33000 AND COALESCE(A.VEHICLE_TYPE,'') <> ('EQUIPMENT') THEN CAST('MEDIUM DUTY' AS VARCHAR(50)) WHEN (A.GVWR IS NULL OR A.GVWR = 0) AND UPPER(A.VEHICLE_TRIM) IN ('MEDIUM DUTY') THEN CAST('MEDIUM DUTY' AS VARCHAR(50)) WHEN A.GVWR > 33000 AND COALESCE(A.VEHICLE_TYPE,'') <> ('EQUIPMENT') THEN CAST('HEAVY DUTY' AS VARCHAR(50)) WHEN (A.GVWR IS NULL OR A.GVWR = 0) AND UPPER(A.VEHICLE_TRIM) IN ('CAB & CHASSIS','HEAVY DUTY','TRACTOR') THEN CAST('HEAVY DUTY' AS VARCHAR(50)) WHEN UPPER(A.VEHICLE_TRIM) IN ('TRACTOR') THEN CAST('HEAVY DUTY' AS VARCHAR(50)) WHEN (A.GVWR IS NULL OR A.GVWR = 0) AND M.MARKET_CLASS IS NOT NULL THEN CAST(M.MC_VEHICLE_TYPE AS VARCHAR(50)) ELSE 'EQUIPMENT' END"

    },
    {

      "join": "LEFT",

    {
      "alias": "LT",

      "ordinal_position": 49,
      "source": "null",
      "target": "AGG_CE",
      "target_type": "EXPOSED",
      "transformation": "CE.AGG_CE"
    },
    {
      "data_type": "NUMBER(18,2)",
      "ordinal_position": 50,
      "source": "null",
      "target": "SELLING_FEE",
      "target_type": "EXPOSED",
      "transformation": "INCLUDED_SELLING_FEE"
    },
    {
      "data_type": "NUMBER(18,2)",
      "ordinal_position": 51,
      "source": "null",
      "target": "PRINCIPAL_RENT",
      "target_type": "EXPOSED",
      "transformation": "ASSET_VALUE - RESIDUAL_VALUE"
    },
    {
      "data_type": "NUMBER(18,2)",
      "ordinal_position": 52,
      "source": "null",
      "target": "SECURITIZATION_VALUE",
      "target_type": "EXPOSED",
      "transformation": "ASSET_VALUE + RECV_VALUE + DEPOSIT_VALUE"
    },
    {
      "data_type": "NUMBER(18,2)",
      "ordinal_position": 53,
      "source": "null",
      "target": "AGG_SV",
      "target_type": "EXPOSED",
      "transformation": "SUM(ASSET_VALUE + RECV_VALUE + DEPOSIT_VALUE) OVER (PARTITION BY WAV.CALC_DT, WAV.ASSET_ID)"
    },
    {
      "data_type": "NUMBER(18,2)",
      "ordinal_position": 54,
      "source": "null",
      "target": "OBLIGOR_ENHANCEMENT_VALUE",
      "target_type": "EXPOSED",
      "transformation": "ROUND(COALESCE((SECURITIZATION_VALUE/NULLIF(AGG_SV,0)),0)*COALESCE(AGG_CE,0),2)"
    },
    {
      "data_type": "NUMBER(18,2)",
      "ordinal_position": 55,
      "source": "null",
      "target": "OE_REDUCED_SV",
      "target_type": "EXPOSED",
      "transformation": "SECURITIZATION_VALUE - OBLIGOR_ENHANCEMENT_VALUE"
    },
    {
      "data_type": "NUMBER(18,2)",
      "ordinal_position": 56,
      "source": "null",
      "target": "RESIDUAL_VALUE_REDUCED_SV",
      "target_type": "EXPOSED",
      "transformation": "SECURITIZATION_VALUE - RESIDUAL_VALUE"
    },
    {
      "data_type": "NUMBER(18,2)",
      "ordinal_position": 57,
      "source": "null",
      "target": "ADJUSTED_SV",
      "target_type": "EXPOSED",
      "transformation": "SECURITIZATION_VALUE - OBLIGOR_ENHANCEMENT_VALUE - RESIDUAL_VALUE"
    }
  ],
  "delete_filter": "CALC_DT = '{{ V_CALC_DT }}' ",
  "joins": [
    {
      "alias": "V",
      "on": "WAV.CALC_DT = V.CALC_DT AND WAV.ASSET_ID = V.ASSET_ID",
      "table": "CLIENT_STAGE_T.WHEELS_VEHICLE_DATA",
      "type": "LEFT"
    },
    {
      "alias": "C",
      "on": "WAV.CALC_DT = C.CALC_DT AND WAV.FLEET_ID::VARCHAR = C.FLEET_ID::VARCHAR",
      "table": "CLIENT_STAGE_T.WHEELS_CLIENT_DATA",
      "type": "LEFT"
    },
    {
      "alias": "L",
      "on": "UPPER(V.LEASE_TYPE) = L.LEASE_TYPE_INPUT AND WAV.CALC_DT >= L.START_DT AND WAV.CALC_DT < L.END_DT",
      "table": "CONFIG_LKP.LKP_LEASE_TYPE",
      "type": "LEFT"
    },
    {
      "alias": "F",
      "on": "WAV.ASSET_SALE_ID::VARCHAR = F.FLEETCO_ID_INPUT AND WAV.CALC_DT >= F.START_DT AND WAV.CALC_DT < F.END_DT",
      "table": "CONFIG_LKP.LKP_ETL_STAGE_FLEETCO_ID",
      "type": "INNER"
    },
    {
      "alias": "VEH_INELIG",
      "on": "WAV.ASSET_ID = VEH_INELIG.ASSET_ID AND WAV.CALC_DT = VEH_INELIG.CALC_DT",
      "table": "(SELECT CALC_DT,ASSET_ID,LISTAGG(DISTINCT INELIGIBLE_DESC,',') AS INELIGIBLE_DESC FROM FLL_CORE_T.INELIGIBLE WHERE   CALC_DT=DATE'2025-04-09' GROUP BY ALL)",
      "type": "LEFT"
    },
    {
      "alias": "CE",
      "on": "UPPER(C.FLEET_ID)|| '-W' = CE.OBLIGOR_ID",
      "table": "(SELECT CALC_DT,OBLIGOR_ID::VARCHAR AS OBLIGOR_ID, SUM(ENHANCEMENT_AMT) AS AGG_CE FROM FLL_CORE_T.OBLIGOR_ENHANCEMENT WHERE CALC_DT = DATE'2025-04-09' GROUP BY ALL)",
      "type": "LEFT"
    }
  ],
  "load_filter": "WAV.CALC_DT = '{{ V_CALC_DT }}'",

  "source_table": "CLIENT_STAGE_T.WHEELS_ASSET_VALUES",

  "load_filter": "CALC_DT = '{{ V_CALC_DT }}'",
  "source_alias": "src",
  "source_table": "(--REDUCED AND ADJUSTED SV--\nSELECT \nSUBQ.*\n                                                    \n-- STEP 1\n\n,GREATEST(ASSET_VALUE + INCLUDED_SELLING_FEE,0) AS ASSET_VALUE_FINAL\n    \n,INCLUDED_SELLING_FEE AS SELLING_FEE\n,CASE \nWHEN ASSET_VALUE - RESIDUAL_VALUE < 0 \n    THEN 0 \n    ELSE ASSET_VALUE - RESIDUAL_VALUE \nEND AS PRINCIPAL_RENT_STEP_1\t\n,\nPRINCIPAL_RENT_RECV_VALUE \n+ TRAC_RECV_VALUE \n+ ASSUMED_PRINCIPAL_RENT_RECV_VALUE \n+ ASSUMED_TRAC_RECV_VALUE \n    AS RECV_VALUE\n    \n,ASSET_VALUE_SOURCE || COALESCE(' + ' || RECV_VALUE_CALC,'')  AS SECURITIZATION_VALUE_CALC\n\n-- STEP 2\n,'PRORATED ASSET PERCENTAGE' AS OBLIGOR_ENHANCEMENT_VALUE_CALC\n,CE.AGG_CE\n\n-- STEP 3\n,ASSET_VALUE - RESIDUAL_VALUE AS PRINCIPAL_RENT\t\n,ASSET_VALUE + RECV_VALUE + DEPOSIT_VALUE AS SECURITIZATION_VALUE\n,SUM(ASSET_VALUE + RECV_VALUE + DEPOSIT_VALUE) OVER (PARTITION BY CALC_DT, ASSET_ID) AS AGG_SV\n\n-- STEP 4\n,ROUND(\tCOALESCE( ( SECURITIZATION_VALUE / NULLIF(AGG_SV,0) ) , 0 ) -- PRORATED PERCENTAGE\n                *\n    COALESCE(AGG_CE,0) -- AGGREGATE AMOUNT\n                , 2)  -- ROUNDED TO TWO DECIMALS (MAY CAUSE NOT MATERIAL PENNY ROUNDING ISSUES) CAN BE SOLVED WITH SOME EXTRA LOGIC IF NECESSARY\n                AS OBLIGOR_ENHANCEMENT_VALUE\n\n,SECURITIZATION_VALUE_CALC AS SV_CALC\n,SECURITIZATION_VALUE AS SV_AMT\n,OBLIGOR_ENHANCEMENT_VALUE_CALC AS OE_VALUE_CALC\n,OBLIGOR_ENHANCEMENT_VALUE AS OE_ASSET_AMT\n,SECURITIZATION_VALUE - OBLIGOR_ENHANCEMENT_VALUE AS OE_REDUCED_SV \n,SECURITIZATION_VALUE - RESIDUAL_VALUE AS RESIDUAL_VALUE_REDUCED_SV \n,SECURITIZATION_VALUE - OBLIGOR_ENHANCEMENT_VALUE - RESIDUAL_VALUE AS ADJUSTED_SV                                         \t\t\t\t\t\t\t    \n        \nFROM \n(   \n    --GATHER ELEMENTS AND START CALCULATIONS--\n    SELECT \n        ASSET_WT.CALC_DT\n        ,ASSET_WT.ASSET_ID\n        ,ASSET_WT.FLEETCO_ID\n        ,CASE \n            WHEN VEH_INELIG.ASSET_ID IS NOT NULL THEN 1\n            ELSE 0 \n        END AS INELIGIBLE_IND\n        \n        , CASE \t\n            WHEN ASSET_WT.IN_PROCESS_IND = 'YES' THEN 1      \n            WHEN COALESCE(ASSET_WT.SOLD_DT,DATE'2099-12-31') > ASSET_WT.CALC_DT::DATE\n                AND ( NULLIF(ASSET_WT.PAYMENT_DT,'1900-01-01') <= ASSET_WT.CALC_DT::DATE OR NULLIF(ASSET_WT.INCEPTION_DT,'1900-01-01') <= ASSET_WT.CALC_DT::DATE)\n                \n            THEN 1 \n\n            WHEN COALESCE(ASSET_WT.SOLD_DT,'2099-12-31') <= ASSET_WT.CALC_DT                                                                 \n            AND \n                (\n                    COALESCE(PRINCIPAL_AR.RECV_BALANCE_AMT,0) <> 0 \n                    OR\n                    COALESCE(TRAC_AR.RECV_BALANCE_AMT,0) <> 0 \n                    OR \n                    (COALESCE(ASSET_WT.DISPOSITION_PROCEEDS,0) = 0 AND ASSET_WT.ASSET_JSON:LL_ID_A::STRING = ASSET_WT.ASSET_JSON:LL_ID_L::STRING)                \n                )\n            THEN 1\n            ELSE 0 \n        END AS LL_ACTIVE_IND\n\n        ,ASSET_WT.LL_TYPE\n                \n\n        ,CASE                                                   \n                \n            WHEN COALESCE(ASSET_WT.SOLD_DT,DATE'2099-12-31') <= ASSET_WT.CALC_DT::DATE\n                AND ASSET_WT.LL_TYPE= 'CLOSED END'   \n                AND COALESCE(ASSET_WT.DISPOSITION_PROCEEDS,0) = 0\n            THEN CAST('SOLD CLOSED + NO PROCEEDS' AS VARCHAR(50))    \n                                                                    \n            WHEN COALESCE(ASSET_WT.SOLD_DT,DATE'2099-12-31') <= ASSET_WT.CALC_DT::DATE                            \n                AND ASSET_WT.LL_TYPE= 'OPEN END'      \n                AND COALESCE(ASSET_WT.DISPOSITION_PROCEEDS,0) = 0\n            THEN CAST('SOLD OPEN + NO PROCEEDS' AS VARCHAR(50))\n\n            WHEN COALESCE(ASSET_WT.SOLD_DT,DATE'2099-12-31') <= ASSET_WT.CALC_DT::DATE  \n                AND COALESCE(ASSET_WT.DISPOSITION_PROCEEDS,0) <> 0\n            THEN CAST('ASSET SOLD' AS VARCHAR(50))\n\n            WHEN COALESCE(ASSET_WT.LL_NBV,0) > 0                   \n            THEN CAST('BOOK VALUE >0' AS VARCHAR(50))\n\n            WHEN COALESCE(ASSET_WT.LL_NBV,0) <= 0                   \n                AND COALESCE(ASSET_WT.LL_CAP_COST_AMT,0) > 0     \n                AND COALESCE(ASSET_WT.CURRENT_TERM_MONTHS_BILLED,0) > 0 \n            THEN  CAST('FULLY DEPRECIATED'  AS VARCHAR(50))\n\n            WHEN COALESCE(ASSET_WT.LL_NBV,0) <= 0                   \n                AND COALESCE(ASSET_WT.LL_CAP_COST_AMT,0) > 0         \n                AND COALESCE(ASSET_WT.TERMINATION_DT,DATE'2099-12-31') <=  ASSET_WT.CALC_DT::DATE\n            THEN CAST('FULLY DEPRECIATED'  AS VARCHAR(50))\n\n            WHEN COALESCE(ASSET_WT.LL_CAP_COST_AMT,0) > 0           \n                THEN  CAST('CAP COST'   AS VARCHAR(50))\n\n            WHEN ASSET_WT.IN_PROCESS_IND = 'YES' THEN 'ACCT_CAP_COST_AMT'   -- 2024-03-12 added for in-process units where LEASE_LOAN values are null\n\n                ELSE  CAST('PURCHASE PRICE'  AS VARCHAR(50))\n        END AS ASSET_VALUE_SOURCE\n\n        , COALESCE(CASE                                                                 \n\n            WHEN COALESCE(ASSET_WT.SOLD_DT,DATE'2099-12-31') <= ASSET_WT.CALC_DT::DATE              \n                AND ASSET_WT.LL_TYPE= 'CLOSED END'\n                AND COALESCE(ASSET_WT.DISPOSITION_PROCEEDS,0) = 0\n            THEN LEAST(ASSET_WT.LL_NBV,ASSET_WT.RESIDUAL_VALUE) \n            \n            WHEN COALESCE(ASSET_WT.SOLD_DT,DATE'2099-12-31') <= ASSET_WT.CALC_DT::DATE \n                AND ASSET_WT.LL_TYPE= 'OPEN END'       \n                AND COALESCE(ASSET_WT.DISPOSITION_PROCEEDS,0) = 0\n            THEN ASSET_WT.LL_NBV \n            \n            WHEN COALESCE(ASSET_WT.SOLD_DT,DATE'2099-12-31') <= ASSET_WT.CALC_DT::DATE   \n                AND COALESCE(ASSET_WT.DISPOSITION_PROCEEDS,0) <> 0\n            THEN 0 \n            \n            WHEN COALESCE(ASSET_WT.LL_NBV,0) > 0                    \n            THEN COALESCE(ASSET_WT.LL_NBV,0)                      \n            \n            WHEN COALESCE(ASSET_WT.LL_NBV,0) <= 0                  \n                AND COALESCE(ASSET_WT.LL_CAP_COST_AMT,0) > 0     \n                AND COALESCE(ASSET_WT.CURRENT_TERM_MONTHS_BILLED,0) > 0 \n            THEN COALESCE(ASSET_WT.LL_NBV,0)\n\n            WHEN COALESCE(ASSET_WT.LL_NBV,0) <= 0                   \n                AND COALESCE(ASSET_WT.LL_CAP_COST_AMT,0) > 0         \n                AND COALESCE(ASSET_WT.TERMINATION_DT,DATE'2099-12-31') <=  ASSET_WT.CALC_DT::DATE\n            THEN  COALESCE(ASSET_WT.LL_NBV,0)\n            \n            WHEN COALESCE(ASSET_WT.LL_CAP_COST_AMT,0) > 0         \n            THEN COALESCE(ASSET_WT.LL_CAP_COST_AMT,0) + ({{ INCLUDE_UPFIT_COST }}* COALESCE(ASSET_WT.UPFIT_COST,0))\n            \n            WHEN ASSET_WT.IN_PROCESS_IND = 'YES' THEN COALESCE(ASSET_WT.ASSET_JSON:ACCT_CAP_COST_AMT::NUMBER(18,2),ASSET_WT.PURCHASE_PRICE)   -- 2024-03-12 added for in-process units where LEASE_LOAN values are null                                                                                  ELSE COALESCE(ASSET_WT.ASSET_JSON:ACCT_CAP_COST_AMT::NUMBER(18,2),ASSET_WT.PURCHASE_PRICE)\n            ELSE COALESCE(ASSET_WT.ACCT_CAP_COST_AMT,ASSET_WT.PURCHASE_PRICE)\n                \n        END,0) AS ASSET_VALUE                                                 -- 2024-03-20 added coalesce for OEM purchases with null ACCT_CAP_COST\n                    \n        , COALESCE(CASE                                                     -- 2024-03-20 added coalesce for in-process units that have null RESIDUAL_VALUE\n            WHEN COALESCE(ASSET_WT.SOLD_DT,DATE'2099-12-31') <= ASSET_WT.CALC_DT::DATE\n                THEN 0 \n                \n            WHEN ASSET_WT.LL_TYPE= 'OPEN END'             \n                THEN 0 \n                \n                ELSE LEAST(ASSET_WT.LL_NBV,ASSET_WT.RESIDUAL_VALUE) \n            END,0) AS RESIDUAL_VALUE \n        , ASSET_WT.SOLD_DT\n        , ASSET_WT.SELLING_FEE\n        ,\n        CASE \n            WHEN ASSET_WT.LL_TYPE= 'OPEN END' \n                AND COALESCE(ASSET_WT.SOLD_DT,DATE'2099-12-31') > ASSET_WT.CALC_DT::DATE\n                AND {{ INCLUDE_SELLING_FEE }} = 1\n            THEN COALESCE(ASSET_WT.SELLING_FEE,0) \n            ELSE 0 \n            END AS INCLUDED_SELLING_FEE\n        \n        ,'OPEN PRINCIPAL RENT' AS RECV_VALUE_CALC\n        ,COALESCE(PRINCIPAL_AR.RECV_BALANCE_AMT,0) AS PRINCIPAL_RENT_RECV_VALUE\n        ,COALESCE(NULL,0) AS ASSUMED_PRINCIPAL_RENT_RECV_VALUE\n        ,COALESCE(TRAC_AR.RECV_BALANCE_AMT,0) AS TRAC_RECV_VALUE\n        ,COALESCE(NULL,0) AS ASSUMED_TRAC_RECV_VALUE\n        ,0 AS DEPOSIT_VALUE\n        ,'CALCULATED' AS RECORD_SOURCE\n        ,COALESCE(\n            NULLIF(ASSET_WT.ASSET_JSON:RECORD_SOURCE_L::STRING,'BULK')   || ' ON LEASE OR LOAN INPUT DATA' \n            ,NULLIF(ASSET_WT.ASSET_JSON:RECORD_SOURCE_A::STRING,'BULK') || ' ON ASSET INPUT DATA' \n            ,'CALCULATED' \n            ) AS RECORD_NOTE         \n        ,ASSET_WT.ASSET_JSON\n        ,ASSET_WT.RECV_JSON\n        ,IND.INDICATOR_JSON\n        ,VEH_INELIG.INELIGIBLE_JSON                                           \n            \n    FROM \n    CLIENT_STAGE_T.ASSET_WT \n\n    LEFT OUTER JOIN \n    CLIENT_STAGE_T.AGG_RECV_WT PRINCIPAL_AR \n    ON ASSET_WT.CALC_DT = PRINCIPAL_AR.CALC_DT \n    AND ASSET_WT.FLEETCO_ID = PRINCIPAL_AR.FLEETCO_ID \n    AND ASSET_WT.ASSET_ID = PRINCIPAL_AR.ASSET_ID \n    AND PRINCIPAL_AR.RECV_TYPE = 'PRINCIPAL_AR'\n\n    LEFT OUTER JOIN \n    CLIENT_STAGE_T.AGG_RECV_WT TRAC_AR \n    ON ASSET_WT.CALC_DT = TRAC_AR.CALC_DT \n    AND ASSET_WT.FLEETCO_ID = TRAC_AR.FLEETCO_ID \n    AND ASSET_WT.ASSET_ID = TRAC_AR.ASSET_ID \n    AND TRAC_AR.RECV_TYPE = 'TRAC_AR'\n\n    LEFT OUTER JOIN \n    FLL_STAGE_T.INELIGIBLE_FLATTENED VEH_INELIG\n    ON ASSET_WT.ASSET_ID = VEH_INELIG.ASSET_ID\n    AND ASSET_WT.CALC_DT = VEH_INELIG.CALC_DT    \n\n    LEFT OUTER JOIN\n    FLL_STAGE_T.INDICATOR_FLATTENED IND\n    ON IND.ASSET_ID = ASSET_WT.ASSET_ID\n    AND IND.CALC_DT = ASSET_WT.CALC_DT\n    \n    WHERE ASSET_WT.CALC_DT = '{{ V_CALC_DT }}' \n    AND ASSET_WT.FLEETCO_ID = {{ FLEETCO_ID }}\n\n) SUBQ\n                                                    \nLEFT OUTER JOIN\n(\n    SELECT OBLIGOR_ID, SUM(ENHANCEMENT_AMT) AS AGG_CE\n    FROM\n    FLL_CORE_T.OBLIGOR_ENHANCEMENT \n    WHERE CALC_DT = '{{ V_CALC_DT }}'\n    GROUP BY OBLIGOR_ID\n) CE\nON CE.OBLIGOR_ID = SUBQ.ASSET_JSON:OBLIGOR_ID::STRING)",
  "target_table": "CLIENT_STAGE_T.CE_SV_LEDGER_MT_TEST"
}
